<h3 id="using-admonitions">Using Admonitions</h3>

<p>Hereâ€™s a handy feature: You can enable an extension to use <a href="https://python-markdown.github.io/extensions/admonition/">admonitions</a> in MkDocs. This is a quick and easy way to start using notes, warnings, and tips on your MkDocs site. See this <a href="https://github.com/mkdocs/mkdocs/issues/1659">GitHub issue</a> for more information and examples.</p>

